item.description:
@Helbound wrote:

Hey, thats 2 errors less, lol. And could you copy what the compiler says down and post it here? If you don’t know how, then here-

  1. Right click somewhere in your compiler (preferably in black, empty space.)
  2. Click “Select All”
  3. Without touching the mouse, press your enter key on your keyboard.
  4. Go to: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=post;topic=224947.0;num_replies=7
  5. And type-
Heres the compiler feedback:
  1. Paste the compiler feedback (what you just copied from the compiler) in the comment.

(Not trying to be mean, Its just that some ppl who I think already know how to do this stuff, really don’t. Lol.)
